      ],
      "description": "<p>A <strong>Dazed</strong> creature is recovering from a powerful blow and cannot take as many actions as usual.</p><ul><li><p>A Dazed creature can only either move or take an action, not both.</p></li><li><p>A Dazed creature cannot take a bonus action.</p></li><li><p>The Dazed Condition lasts until the End of the affected creature’s next turn.</p></li></ul>",
